# Node
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/.vite

# Env & secrets — never leak these into images. Real env values are
# passed at runtime (docker --env-file / compose env_file), never baked
# into the image layer. Catches .env, .env.development, .env.production,
# .env.*.local, and the .example templates too.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# Git / editor noise
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea
**/*.swp
**/.DS_Store

# Logs & coverage
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Docs / scripts that don't need to be in the image
**/README*.md
**/CHANGELOG*.md
docs/

# OS-specific generated artifacts
Thumbs.db
